// MobileHeader
// Compact header for the mobile layout. Mirrors the desktop Header's project/
// session management but with icon-only buttons and smaller dropdowns.
// Shows a phase badge (color-coded by session state) and connection dot.

FUNCTION getPhaseColor(session) -> string
  Maps session state/displayName to Tailwind color classes:
    brainstorm -> blue, rough-draft/build-task-graph -> amber,
    execute/ready-to-implement -> green, systematic-debugging -> red,
    done/workflow-complete -> emerald.

---

FUNCTION MobileHeader(onSessionSelect, onCreateSession, onDeleteSession) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Reads sessions, currentSession, registeredProjects, collabState from stores.
  Manages project and session dropdown open state.
  Renders: project selector button, session selector button, phase badge,
  connection dot, theme toggle, refresh button.
  Dropdowns close on click outside or Escape.
  Confirms project removal before calling remove action.

---

FUNCTION handleProjectSelect(project) -> void
  Sets selectedProject. Auto-selects first session or clears if empty.

---

FUNCTION handleSessionClick(session) -> void
  Calls onSessionSelect(session). Closes dropdown.

---

FUNCTION handleThemeToggle() -> void
  Toggles light/dark theme.

---

FUNCTION handleRefreshSessions() -> void
  Reloads session list from API.

---

FUNCTION handleAddProject() -> void
  Prompts for project path, calls api.registerProject.

---

FUNCTION handleRemoveProject(project) -> void
  Confirms with window.confirm, then calls api.unregisterProject.

---

FUNCTION handleCreateSession() -> void
  Calls onCreateSession for selectedProject.

---

FUNCTION handleDeleteSession(session, e) -> void
  Stops propagation. Calls onDeleteSession(session).
